    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Honest fair-condition car with visible wear consistent with age and use. It runs and drives, but it\u2019s not a mint or fully sorted example, and buyers should expect cosmetic imperfections inside and out along with some general signs of use. A practical option for someone looking for affordable transportation or a project to improve over time, best suited for a buyer who values a straightforward, realistically represented car.",
      "price": 18900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept example in good condition and ready to enjoy. It shows nicely, feels solid, and should make a great choice for someone looking for a dependable, presentable car they can drive with confidence. Not a perfect or like-new vehicle, but an honest, attractive driver with a lot to offer.",
      "price": 33900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly vehicle that offers dependable basic transportation and strong value for the money. This car shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but it remains an appealing option for buyers seeking an inexpensive way to get on the road. Priced to sell and ideal for someone comfortable with a well-used vehicle.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with some life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who wants reliable basic transport or a project to tinker with. Priced fairly for what it is, and represented honestly \u2014 a great chance to get into a car without spending a fortune. If you want something cheap, usable, and worth a look, this could be the one.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget daily with good bones and plenty of upside. This car starts, runs, and drives, with a powertrain that feels willing and a chassis that still tracks confidently. Not a show car and it does have cosmetic wear and age-related needs, but it presents as a usable driver for someone who appreciates mechanical simplicity and doesn\u2019t mind turning a wrench. Great candidate for a restoration, commuter, or weekend tinkering platform. Priced to reflect condition while still offering real value for an enthusiast looking for an affordable entry point.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Honest workhorse with plenty of life left. Not pretty, priced right. Great cheap transportation. First serious buyer gets it.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that makes it stand out from cookie-cutter commuters. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who loves a hands-on project, needs an affordable set of wheels, or wants a vehicle with story, grit, and plenty of potential still waiting to be unlocked. If you appreciate machines with soul and can see the beauty in bringing something back to life, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers an affordable way into ownership for the right buyer. Best suited for someone seeking basic transportation, a project, or a parts opportunity, it presents honest budget-car appeal with straightforward value. A smart pick for shoppers who recognize the potential in a low-cost option.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    }
  ],
